I'll wait.

198
00:16:51,970 --> 00:16:53,722
I don't need such a thing...

199
00:16:54,305 --> 00:16:55,890
Just do it!

200
00:16:58,017 --> 00:17:02,897
You wouldn't even be able...
to put one knick on my forehead!

201
00:17:03,690 --> 00:17:04,941
You're wrong!

202
00:17:05,024 --> 00:17:09,446
I'm saying this is a testament to fighting
on equal terms as a Leaf Shinobi!

203
00:17:11,573 --> 00:17:14,159
And I'm saying stuff like that
is acting high and mighty!

204
00:17:14,242 --> 00:17:16,619
Do you think that we're equal?!

205
00:17:16,703 --> 00:17:21,875
Yeah, I do! I've never once
thought that I'm inferior to you!

206
00:17:22,500 --> 00:17:24,085
You're an eyesore!

207
00:17:24,669 --> 00:17:29,090
That's because you remain weak!
Little Sasuke!

208
00:17:29,549 --> 00:17:31,050
Naruto!

209
00:17:31,509 --> 00:17:33,011
Sasuke!

210
00:18:20,517 --> 00:18:21,643
Don't be getting carried away!

211
00:18:38,076 --> 00:18:39,285
Naruto...

212
00:18:43,998 --> 00:18:46,000
Enough already, believe it!

213
00:19:06,145 --> 00:19:09,107
Multi-Shadow Clone Jutsu!

214
00:19:42,223 --> 00:19:44,684
U-zu-ma-ki!

215
00:19:53,902 --> 00:19:55,028
Naruto Barrage!

216
00:20:00,950 --> 00:20:01,951
The Tiger Seal!

217
00:20:03,202 --> 00:20:05,663
Fire Style! Fire Ball Jutsu!

218
00:20:16,591 --> 00:20:17,759
N-Naruto!

219
00:20:29,938 --> 00:20:31,648
Wh-What is that Jutsu?!

220
00:20:37,195 --> 00:20:38,821
Damn it!

221
00:20:40,990 --> 00:20:42,408
Chidori: One Thousand Birds!

222
00:20:44,744 --> 00:20:46,079
